  "ciliary_role": "Essential for pla rian ciliogenesis (19933103). Kif27 expression is upregulated during mouse tracheal epithelial cells differentiation, consistent with their essential roles in motile ciliogenesis (19305393). Interacts with Fu and both may regulate central pair assembly, probably through the recruitment or activation of central pair proteins such as Spag16 and Pcdp1. It could also interact with basal body components or accessory structures in controlling cilia orientation (23907739).",
